abstract.value: The <title ns2:type="simple" render="italic">0 to 9</title> Archive is a collection of correspondence and manuscripts to the editors of <title ns2:type="simple" render="italic">0 to 9</title> magazine, Vito Hannibal Acconci and Bernadette Mayer. <title ns2:type="simple" render="italic">0 to 9</title> was a small avant garde literary magazine from the late 1960s.

p.value: Materials are open to researchers. Please contact the Fales Library and Special Collections, fales.library@nyu.edu, 212-998-2596.

Published citations should take the following form: <lb/><lb/>Identification of item, date (if known); 0 to 9 Archive; MSS 026; box number; folder number; <address><addressline>Fales Library and Special Collections</addressline></address>, New York University Libraries.
